        src="/images/logo-inverted.svg"
        alt="Cools inverted logo"
      />
      <p class="text-[#E5E5E5] w-5/6 mb-5">
        Cools is a bunch of useful and fun tools that you can use for your
        purposes
      </p>

      <div class="md:flex flex-col hidden font-[Koulen] text-2xl">
        My contacts:
        <ul class="text-base leading-10">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="flex gap-3 items-center">
              <svg
